metadata.name: Juggling Act
metadata.description:
This 1:1 Dark Side Elephant I recreated using Adobe Illustrator and is the first piece in my collection called 'rent'. The original picture was drawn with a pen and I took that image and lowered the opacity on AI to create this and one other with a White background. 

In 2014 I was working at Yard House in Denver, CO as a host. This was at a point in my life where I was a different person, it's been a juggling act to get to where I'm at today. Elephants are some of the most intelligent and delicate creatures, something I admire very much. 

This is my first piece I'm putting up for sale in a space that for some reason keeps pulling me in even when everything is telling me to leave.
